              <DefinitionShort>a stall where animals are fed</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>stall</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>φάτνη[b] may designate a part of a barn, or it may simply refer to a customary place where an animal is fed outside, often in a semi-enclosure (see {D:6.137}).</Comments>
